Where can i watch the installation video guide? There is a QR code on the box where the phone film is packed, you can watch the installation video by scanning the QR code. The flexibility of the glass screen protector is the same as the plastic material, is it tempered glass or plastic? This screen protector is a real tempered glass. The plastic flexibility is the exact reason why we call it tempered glass screen protector. Tempered glass is a type of safety glass that is stronger than ordinary glass. How can I remove bubbles? Use the kit in the package to clean the screen before placing the screen protector.If there are bubbles, try to gently press the bubbles with your finger or with a ruler,but the screen surface needs a thin cloth pad to avoid scratching the protector. How can I remove a cracked glass screen protector? Lift the screen protector with the card from any corner of the screen protector, then hold the corner and remove slowly. (If you find CHIP or CRACK on the screen protector, for your safety, please wear gloves when removing the screen protector.) Does this work with the fingerprint reader? Yes it works. After installing the screen protector slightly moisten your finger tip before adding the finger print security option to your phone. There is a video to guide you in the product description.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 31, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Saved My Phone
reviews.reviewText: I've had this screen protector on my phone for 8 months. It was very easy to install, and the fit was perfect for my Samsung Galaxy S23.Tonight, this protector really earned its namesake, along with my undying gratitude. My pants pocket betrayed me, and my phone fell HARD (screen side down, of course) onto unrelenting concrete. 'Tis the season to be merry, but instead of sugerplums dancing in my head, I envisioned a trip to Verizon to get my screen fixed. However, what to my wondering eyes should appear, but a CRACK-FREE screen when I lifted the protector off my phone. The cover itself took the brunt of the hit and cracked as shown in the image, but my phone screen was completely pristine.The icing on the sugar cookie is that this protector comes in a pack of 2. I just installed its twin (RIP Protector 1 - lost, but not forgotten). I'm looking forward to a new year where my first resolution is to get rid of these traitorous pants!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 15, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This is the best screen protector I have ever used and instalation was a breeze. Not only does the company have QR codes to easily find your installation video, there is also a small instructions paper on how to adjust your fingerprint reader. I absolutely love the frame that came with the protector it has made installing the protector so easy and I didn't have any bubbles. This also comes with a tool to remove them if you get them. This will be the brand I go to from now on they covered everything needed and packaging is amazing too!Edit: I dropped my phone in the driveway. The picture above was the aftermath of the screen protector. This screen protector worked perfectly, there's not a single crack or chip in my phone screen! 10/10 I will be buying again.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars True to form advertisement
reviews.reviewText: The product is very good. Smooth, durable, easy installation. My biggest complaint, however, is that I was looking for a screen protector that did not have a cut out for the front facing camera. I wanted one that was full coverage. The pictures made it appear as though there was no cut out, but there is in fact a front facing camera cut out. If a full coverage screen protector is important to you, this is not the product for you. However, if that doesn't matter, then this is a great choice!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great customer service
reviews.reviewText: The screen protector went on easy and I had no issues with the fingerprint reader or other touch features. 6 months after putting the protector on, I dropped the phone going up some stairs and was expecting the worst. While the protector had spider-cracks on the surface, the phone still worked, and the screen underneath was intact. I contacted UniqueMe for help and they are replacing the protector with no issues. Very responsive throughout the process.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Protector cracked with a single drop... AGAIN
reviews.reviewText: Update: Nope! I Installed a second protector after the first shattered. It lasted about a week before it too shattered. These things are just too darn brittle and shatter far too easily. The lens cover I applied at the time time also popped off a couple days later. Do not recommend!*****I've purchased several different screen protectors over the years. When I got my new Samsung Galaxy S23 earlier this year, I picked this particular protector mostly for the fact that it came with an easy-install frame. The installation was simple and the protector looked great. Within a couple months I dropped the phone on some tile and it shattered. I actually thought it was the screen that shattered and assumed the protector was the only thing holding it together, so I didn't attempt to remove the protector until I knew I could find time to get the screen replaced. However, soon after, bits of the protector started to chip off and I realized, thankfully, it was just the protector that had shattered. I've never shattered a screen or a protector before. The protector was a little bit difficult to remove, but I peeled it off and put on #2 in the pack. Unfortunately, although I was super careful, these things are so staticky, I got a tiny spec of lint under the protector right in the center and it looks awful. Other than that, installation was again nearly fool proof. I'm not sure I'd purchase this brand again as its much more brittle than others I've used, but if you find installation daunting, you may like this one **while it lasts.** My previous brand of protector offered lifetime replacement (which I did need to use once), so I think I may switch back to that one now that I have a different model phone.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Saved my screen several times
reviews.reviewText: I've gone through 4 of these protectors on my Galaxy S21 Plus over the past 2 years. I have dropped my phone several times. When the protector cracks, I take off the broken one and put on a new one. These have saved me from having to buy a new phone several times. My only complaint is sometimes my fingerprint reader doesn't work as well as when I don't have a screen protector on.

The S23 screen protector 2-pack has been an essential safeguard for my smartphone's display. These protectors offer outstanding scratch resistance, effectively shielding my phone's screen from the wear and tear of daily use. The 2-pack is a bonus, providing a spare protector for future use or for sharing with a friend or family member. The installation process was straightforward, thanks to the included cleaning kit and precise instructions, which ensured a bubble-free and flawless application. Once applied, the screen protector is virtually invisible, preserving the clarity and touch sensitivity of my phone's screen without any distortion.What I appreciate most about the S23 screen protectors is their durability. Even after months of use, the protector has remained scratch-free and clear, maintaining the pristine appearance of my smartphone's display. The oleophobic coating helps repel fingerprints and smudges, reducing the need for constant cleaning. The 2-pack ensures that I have a backup in case the first one ever needs replacement, offering long-term protection and peace of mind. Overall, the S23 screen protector 2-pack is a reliable and cost-effective solution for safeguarding your smartphone's screen from daily wear and tear, and I highly recommend it to anyone looking to keep their device looking and functioning like new.

I love the UniqueMe screen protectors. I love that they are tempered glass and having 2 of them helps in case the first one didn't work out or if it breaks at some point. Also like how they have camera protectors too. I've used them for my S21 and now for my s23+. Super easy to install (no bubbles might I add). No glare or anything. I don't use the fingerprint reader, so I cannot comment on that, but super easy to install and well worth the purchase. I highly recommend :)
